網站[「開放民主」](http://www.opendemocracy.net/
"http://www.opendemocracy.net/")刊載了羅伯特·錢德勒與伊莉莎白·錢德勒夫婦[翻譯的〈長路〉（ _The Road_
暫譯）](http://www.opendemocracy.net/od-russia/robert-chandler/vasily-grossmans-
road "http://www.opendemocracy.net/od-russia/robert-chandler/vasily-grossmans-
road")，這是俄國作家[瓦西里·葛羅斯曼](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vasily_Grossman
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vasily_Grossman")的短篇小說。[羅伯特·錢德勒並撰文](http://www.opendemocracy.net/od-
russia/robert-chandler/after-life-and-fate-vasily-grossman%E2%80%99s-last-
stories "http://www.opendemocracy.net/od-russia/robert-chandler/after-life-
and-fate-vasily-grossman%E2%80%99s-last-
stories")討論葛羅斯曼的小說及其與[安德烈‧普拉托諾夫](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrei_Platonov
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrei_Platonov")的友誼。

校對：[Portnoy](http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Portnoy
"使用者:Portnoy")

